    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Petasii </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Eximiae integritatis et <lb n="2"/>inconparabilis prudentiae <lb n="3"/>ac totius bonitatis viro <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Petasio <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimo</ex></expan> ex praesidibus <lb n="5"/>provinciae Tripolitanae <lb n="6"/>ordo splendidissimae <lb n="7"/>civitatis Lepcimagnensis <lb n="8"/>decreto suo et populi <lb n="9"/>sufragiis memor me<lb break="no" n="10"/>ritorum in se ab eius prae<lb break="no" n="11"/>stantia conlatorum <lb n="12"/>statuam in foro novo Seve<lb break="no" n="13"/>riano ad perpetuitatis memo<lb break="no" n="14"/>riam patrono dignissimo </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> posuit
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Interpunktion: Palmette. Base used three times: IRT 566 is carved over the first erased text; another erased text on the left side.</p>
            </div>
